Lone Star State of Mind;;2002;;PG-13;;Comedy,Crime;;6.1;;David Semel;;Joshua Jackson,Jaime King,Matthew Davis,Ryan Hurst,John Mellencamp,DJ Qualls,Sam McMurray,Thomas Haden Church,Jullian Dulce Vida,Elizabeth Barondes,Rodger Boyce,Eleese Lester,Tyler Waldrop,Juan Gabriel Pareja,Brian Orr,Larry Hovis,Krista Betts,Ellar Coltrane;;Earl's engaged to his step-sister Baby. Baby has entrusted him to take care of her misfit cousin Junior. Baby is also intent on leaving Texas for LA on Tuesday. When Junior and his recently released ex-con friend Tinker rob a pizza delivery boy and end up with $20,000 of drug money Earl is forced onto the scene, giving up his and Baby's LA money to save Juniors limbs.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0269483/